{
  "stem": "1292.4",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I also remember, once, I bent down while the machine was going, the polishing machine.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And it took a bit of my hair.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And I was almost scalped.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And I still have here a passage what is missing from that time, because it took out the hair with the roots.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The condition.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Well--",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "There was this SS woman who did enjoy eating a bread roll with ham, which was to us then smelling like something out of this world.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I had been very hungry.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I'll never forget this, how I hated for her to eat it so ostentatious, like to give us the dig.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But there was soup, and the soup was much thicker, in the evening.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And there was a portion of bread, which was very much guarded, because it wasn't so much of.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And the work-- I remember one young lady who was a great pianist.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And she was put to work on the metal cutting machine.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And well, being not skilled and whatever, it amputated her four fingers.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "It did-- she-- and I remember the tragedy that was for her, being a pianist, because she also was hoping to survive, that she would never be able to play piano.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And there was a typhoid fever when we came, because I remember-- [LAUGHS] I must have been a very strong person and have--",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--wonderful resistance.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I had been, I think, 23. 23?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Must have had wonderful resistance, because this girl sleeping next to me, she did have typhoid fever, I remember.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "She was one lovely girl.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "She was a daughter of a doctor.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And she was a lovely looking, gentle girl.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And she was very feverish.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And we were sleeping like sardines, you know, on this straw.",
      "word_count": 11
    }
  ],
